{"tid":1737923,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"美國您都算為香港人講盡好說話。 星期日變相公投唔可以失去","createTime":"2019-11-19T05:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T05:50:19.000Z","uid":283725,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b41ab39c89eb679ffacb2408fd25f912420ca4aa","tid":1737923,"uid":283725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"美國國務卿蓬佩奧透過美國駐港總領事館，向傳媒發新聞稿，表示美方對目前香港持續不斷深化的社會衝突與暴力事件，包括近日在理工大學的警民對峙，表達嚴重關切，促請雙方保持克制，任何一方的暴力都不能接受。<br />\n<br />\n蓬佩奧表示，特區政府有著根本性的責任，為本港回復平靜。特區政府必須回應社會訴求，包括要求特首林鄭月娥在監警會外，成立獨立調查委員會，以增強問責性，並再次呼籲北京履行《中英聯合聲明》中的承諾，保護香港的自由、法律制度和民主生活方式。"},{"pid":"e3ded7cdf00505ee6f8a0731c7bf0a22f871272f","tid":1737923,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\n【行動】Twitter 戰線：世界各地政要火力全開！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1737604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1737604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\nTwitter組24小時keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入----------&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=uyJPOiOY0yV7leae1MMhfEB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=ba45611f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務"},{"pid":"74d7c63c4a2465a4fe726f789096f7b212170eda","tid":1737923,"uid":9857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u0HQ6RQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu0HQ6RQ.png&h=6e0c27fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n未完！"},{"pid":"ca63bfcd98705ff4553afddba006a70065547051","tid":1737923,"uid":256837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T05:50:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pn8dkc4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPn8dkc4.jpg&h=39e6138a&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}